cast.overview: Following the latest Ghostface killings, the four survivors leave Woodsboro behind and start a fresh chapter.
cast.title: Scream VI

details.biography: Devyn Nekoda is an actress best known for playing Anika Kayoko in the 6th installment of the Scream Franchise Scream VI (2023). She has been involved in television and film productions since 2014. From 2016 to 2017 she played the role of Vanessa Morita in a total of 60 episodes of the television series Backstage, which was broadcast on Disney Channel, among others. Another major series role she had in Utopia Falls.
details.name: Devyn Nekoda
